3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a novel approach for encoding local-patch descriptors, which can be applied to various AI tasks such as object recognition and image retrieval. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper uses neural networks to learn the local-patch descriptor and proposes a kernelized approach for matching, which falls under the scope of neural and evolutionary computing. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper evaluates the proposed descriptor on standard benchmarks for image matching, which is a common task in multimedia applications.
